---
Enable, disable, or list tools. (Hermes parity: `hermes tools`.)

Usage: tools <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list     List every registered tool and its Skill Manifest summary
  show     Show the full Skill Manifest for one tool
  enable   Enable a tool for the current session and persist the choice
  disable  Disable a tool for the current session and persist the choice
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
